abstract: Green Dot’s executives are seeking an initial public offering that hands Wal-Mart Stores a ninefold paper gain in the debit-card seller, asking for a higher price than investors pay for any of its rivals, Bloomberg News reports.

headline.main: Wal-Mart and Sequoia Set for 801% Gain From I.P.O.
